t: "f'in khiftum min eaduin lakum fslu salat alkhawf mashyn, 'aw rakbyn, ealaa 'ayi hayyat tsttyewnha walaw bal'iyma', 'aw 'iilaa ghyr jihat alqblt, fa'iidha zal khwfkm fsllu salat alamn, wadhkuruu allah fyha, wala tnqswha ean hyytha alaslyt, washkuruu lah ealaa ma ellamkm min 'umur alebadat walahkam maa lam takunuu ealaa eilm bh"